Uses of Package
sudoku

  • Classes in sudoku used by sudoku 
    Class and Description
    CellIndexesPair
    The CellIndexesPair class is used to create a (row, col) pair where row and col are ints Contains final variables because the variables are initiated only once
    SudokuGenerator
    The SudokuGenerator class use the SudokuSolver class to create a full valid Sudoku game Randomly choose a cell and remove the number, then checks using the SudokuSolver class if the sudoku game is still unique
    SudokuGrid
    The sudokuGridPane class creates a 9x9 grid which contains numbers from 1 to 9.
    SudokuSolver
    The SudokuSolver create a full valid sudoku game for an empty table Resolves Sudoku for a table which is not empty
